      "overview": "After a brief ten-year hiatus, Futurama has crawled triumphantly from the cryogenic tube, its full original cast and satirical spirit intact. New viewers will be able to pick up the series from here, while long-time fans will recognize payoffs to decades-long mysteries - including developments in the epic love story of Fry and Leela, the mysterious contents of Nibbler\u0027s litter box, the secret history of evil Robot Santa, and the whereabouts of Kif and Amy\u0027s tadpoles. Meanwhile there\u0027s a whole new pandemic in town as the crew explores the future of vaccines, bitcoin, cancel culture, and streaming TV.",
